{"tid":493629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幾乎冇命】醫生睇30次都斷錯症 男童尿道感染變敗血症","createTime":"2017-12-08T16:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T18:04:11.000Z","uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0dba851a29cd564bd03d7510c64bf7840f26add3","tid":493629,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"【幾乎冇命】醫生睇30次都斷錯症 男童尿道感染變敗血症<br />\n<br />\n英國白金漢郡一名5歲男童兩年前幾乎一命嗚呼，他尿道受到感染，但看了30次都未能找出正確病因，最後更演變成敗血症。<br />\n<br />\n當時3歲的貝利（Jack Baily）如廁出現問題，小便如「花灑」，他的29歲母親安東（Charlotte Anton）帶兒子看了30次醫生，但都只未找出病因。安東說﹕「最後我堅持不懈，貝利被轉介到泌尿科，但醫生認為他沒有問題。」<br />\n<br />\n直至有一次貝利在托兒所感到不適，回家後開始吐血，送院後病情進一步惡化出現抽搐，「貝利開始失去判斷力，分不清楚我是誰，醫生告知我他腎衰竭。」他一度停止呼吸，幸好醫生成功控制病情，之後替貝利驗血，證實他因急性尿道感染導致敗血症。<br />\n<br />\n貝利留醫了11周才出院。但由於他腎功能受損，未來可能要接受透析。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171208/57551958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57551958&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=51cd376e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57551958&h=e18546ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171208/57551958</a>"},{"pid":"b642fe14aac45756491afc6937c689914dd9712d","tid":493629,"uid":134888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"睇同一個醫生30次都冇用仲繼續睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86653bdac9d0818a5ac6d4d558c5aff7a79411f7","tid":493629,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"要做透析，gg"}]}